{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectSignalName"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectSignalName\/notify"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"explicitNotify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", then any call to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If they did pass ","type":"text"},{"code":"explicitNotify","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"text":" call, like this:","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"title":"ObjectSignalName.notify","symbolKind":"case","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"roleHeading":"Case","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:10GLibObject0B10SignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/objectsignalname\/notify"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/ObjectSignalName":{"kind":"symbol","title":"ObjectSignalName","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectSignalName","type":"topic","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ObjectSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ObjectSignalName","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/objectsignalname"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/ObjectSignalName/notify":{"title":"ObjectSignalName.notify","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/objectsignalname\/notify","abstract":[{"text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"text":", et al.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectSignalName\/notify"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","abstract":[],"title":"GLibObject","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject"},"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names":{"url":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","type":"link","title":"canonical parameter names","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"canonical parameter names"}]}}}